description: This Chainlink VRF common Gaston purrs with a rating of 7, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 14, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, Box for East, Stringalong for South, and 3 for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [14 Votes, Common]
